        {
            "title": "捲到香港？｜京東再次挑機HKTVmall 暗諷「只係比85折 有啲孤寒」推「日日8折」優惠搶客",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">內地電商巨頭京東（9618）繼續燒銀紙強勢攻港，再推出「京東超市日日8折」搶客。京東港澳在社交平台發文指，「只係比85折？咁樣真係有啲孤寒」」，雖然帖文未有開名，但擺明是暗諷近日推出的85折優惠的本地龍頭HKTVmall。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">HKTVmall早前推出85折大型優惠，集團副主席兼行政總裁王維基聲稱自己「30年前起家時已打減價戰」，又指HKTVmall坐擁數十億流動資產，沒有負債，每年EBITDA淨賺3億，「我就要睇吓邊個先投降」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-99a9c730-1341-3f12-8981-b72d7f1e7682-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">京東即搬出8折還擊，兼在字裡行間暗諷HKTVmall。京東港澳發文指出，「賺咗香港人咁多年錢，竟然只係比85折？咁樣真係有啲孤寒」，並指「既然要平，就梗係要平到盡」，宣佈京東超市推出「日日8折」優惠，「唔使湊夠幾百蚊，買滿100元即減20元，買滿99元即可免運費送上門」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">HKTVmall回應本地傳媒查詢時指，過去周末的85折優惠活動只是減價戰的起點，未來會每星期甚至每日推出不同的優惠，並會因應市場情況及客戶意見，適時推出更多具吸引力的活動，又強調多年來一向無懼競爭，並相信所有競爭都有助推動香港電子商貿整體發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得留意的是，自京東攻港以來雙方已多次爆發口水戰，先係去年王維基寸爆京東App抄足HKTVmall八九成，以及「買貴就賠」唔包HKTVmall，之後京東就趁HKTVmall母企香港科技探索 （1137）公佈業續後深夜發文贈興，表示「恭喜」HKTVmall 毛利率逾25%，稱京東自營毛利率只有10%左右，反問「大家覺得邊個平啲呢？」</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8D%B2%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%BA%AC%E6%9D%B1%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E6%8C%91%E6%A9%9Fhktvmall-%E6%9A%97%E8%AB%B7-%E5%8F%AA%E4%BF%82%E6%AF%9485%E6%8A%98-%E6%9C%89%E5%95%B2%E5%AD%A4%E5%AF%92-111610129.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 19:30:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "希捷樂觀展望推動存儲類股上漲,AI數據需求激增",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6_CrUd2j8qGyL_GQv5r0.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7I0CN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週三盤前交易中,數據存儲公司股價大幅上漲,此前希捷科技(<span><span>Seagate</span></span> Technology)發布了超出預期的營收和利潤預測,顯示企業在人工智能基礎設施方面的支出依然強勁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間05:53,西部數據(Western Digital)上漲9.7%,SanDisk跳漲6%,美光科技(Micron)上漲近3%,投資者將希捷的樂觀展望視為存儲硬件需求持續強勁的更廣泛指標。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ec2b0717-15af-3e17-824f-b8a83192a2a3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>希捷</span></span>預計第四季度營收為34.5億美元,上下浮動1億美元,遠高於LSEG彙編的分析師普遍預期的31.6億美元。該公司還預測調整後每股收益為5.00美元,上下浮動20美分,而分析師預期為3.97美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一預測反映出企業對數據存儲設備的需求日益增長,因為各公司加速投資人工智能模型及支持這些模型所需的基礎設施,推動了對硬盤和其他數字存儲產品的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"指數級的代幣增長和新興的AI應用正在推動數據加速增長,並增加數據保留需求,\"摩根士丹利分析師表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">存儲需求的上升恰逢內存價格飆升,因為高耗能的數據中心消耗越來越多的高帶寬內存來存儲和處理大量信息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">內存芯片供應的緊張使得各公司競相尋求替代硬件解決方案以支持其AI雄心,這讓希捷等物理硬盤製造商受益。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B8%8C%E6%8D%B7%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E5%AD%98%E5%84%B2%E9%A1%9E%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-ai%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E6%BF%80%E5%A2%9E-105225799.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 18:55:28",
